org.gbif.registry.search

Class SolrAnnotatedDataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.api.model.registry.search.DatasetSearchResult
      • org.gbif.registry.search.SolrAnnotatedDataset

  • public class SolrAnnotatedDataset
extends org.gbif.api.model.registry.search.DatasetSearchResult
    Annotated version of the dataset search result providing the required mapping to the SOLR schema and translation between String to UUID as SOLR does not support UUID well.
